                            <comment id="13426811" author="luwt" created="Wed, 1 Aug 2012 18:46:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tried with 1.7.1, but 1.7.1 can&apos;t load both of the two TTF files.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
