&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14244967" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 12 Dec 2014 23:20:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1645090 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jahewson&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jahewson&quot;&gt;jahewson&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1645090&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1645090&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1372&quot; title=&quot;NullPointerException with loadDescriptorDictionary&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1372&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1372&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Handle monospace width for last hmtx entry&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14244970" author="jahewson" created="Fri, 12 Dec 2014 23:22:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The NPE was due to incorrect handling of the hmtx table. Note that the font still cannot be embedded because it doesn&apos;t have a cmap table, but that&apos;s not our problem to fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
